    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior shows visible wear including some dents and scratches, with minor surface rust in a few spots. The interior has moderate wear with some scuffing on the upholstery and minor trim damage. Mechanically the car runs but has some issues that may require attention in the near term.",
